relevant_findings.description: CIA internal communication marked 'SECRET' dated 10 Dec 1963, shortly after JFK assassination
relevant_findings.direct_quote: RETURN TO CIA, Background Use Only, Do Not Reproduce
relevant_findings.significance: Indicates ongoing sensitive internal communications about high-level matters in the immediate aftermath of the assassination

relevant_findings.description: Reference to planned visit by an individual (name redacted) from 16 to 19 Feb 1964
relevant_findings.direct_quote: PER YOUR DECISION HQS, PLANNED HAVE (REDACTED) VISIT YOU 16 TO 19 FEB 1964 PRIOR HIS RETURN BROS. HQS OFFICER WILL ESCORT.
relevant_findings.significance: Suggests ongoing operational planning and movement of personnel in early 1964
